                                 RELEASE NOTES                                  
                                                                                
    TeamSpeak 3 continues the legacy of the original TeamSpeak communitcation   
    system previously offered in TeamSpeak Classic (1.5) and TeamSpeak 2.       
    TeamSpeak 3 is not merely an extension of its predecessors but rather a     
    complete rewrite in C++ of its proprietary protocol and core technology.    
                                                                                
    With over seven years of experience and leadership in the VoIP sector,      
    out engineers have created a flexible, powerful and scalable solution       
    granting you the ability to customize and tailor your voice communication   
    needs any way you desire. New users and TeamSpeak veterans alike will now   
    enjoy a completely new experience in voice communication using TeamSpeak    
    3's unmatched functionality and powerful new features.                      
                                                                                
    This Release is a continuation of TEAM MESMERiZE's crack, which seems to    
    have been abandoned. The core idea of it still works, so that creating      
    up-to-date binaries is a one-click task for us now.                         
                                                                                
    We are currently working on reverse engineering the KeyGen and Emulator     
    to allow less suspicious licenses to be generated. If you are interested    
    in helping, read the section at the end of the document.

                               INSTALLATION NOTES                               
                                                                                
    1. Download the original Teamspeak3 Server version from                     
       <a href=" http://teamspeak.gameserver.gamed.de/ts3/releases/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://teamspeak.gameserver.gamed.de/ts3/releases/</a> or                   
       <a href=" http://dl.4players.de/ts/releases/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://dl.4players.de/ts/releases/</a> .                                    
    2. Copy the patched binary over the original binary.                        
    3. Add the following entries to your hosts file or firewall(ipconfig):      
        127.0.0.1            accounting.teamspeak.com                           
        127.0.0.1            backupaccounting.teamspeak.com                     
        127.0.0.1            ipcheck.teamspeak.com                              
        127.0.0.1            hardy.teamspeak.4players.de                        
    3. Generate a license key with the keygen and copy it into your server      
        directory.                                                              
    4. Start the Accounting Server Emulator and after some seconds, start your  
        Teamspeak3 Server.                                                      
    5. Everything should work now, if not, try with another binary.             
    6. Still not working? Repeat from step 1.

                                     SUPPORT                                    
                                                                                
    Recently, people have started using the e-mail address below to request     
    help. That is not what it was made for, and the team will now ignore such   
    e-mails on that address. Neither should you spam the webmaster for help,    
    as that will just get your e-mail server banned from all domains s/he       
    has active. Also, don't fucking annoy random people on a public Teamspeak   
    or on Skype. You have been warned. We are not your go-to person for help.   
                                                                                
    READ THE FUCKING INSTALLATION NOTES. They have been tested so many times    
    and always worked. If they didn't work for you, retry until they do.
